title: About
text:
This site has been generated with Quarto, a software tool for scientific technical documentation suitable for different programming languages. To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
COUSIN has also created a practical Quarto workshop, introducing its applications for scientific documentation and publishing.
